title: Pregnant Person Medium Light Skin Tone
description: Represents a person who is pregnant, with a medium light skin tone. It signifies anticipation, new life, and the journey of pregnancy.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the pregnant person emoji with medium-light skin tone is gracefully rendered with Apple's signature soft gradients and realistic lighting, showcasing a gentle curve of the belly and a serene expression. The smooth, rounded edges of their form and attire emphasize a sense of warmth and anticipation. This inclusive emoji, a thoughtful addition on Apple devices, symbolizes pregnancy, new beginnings, and family.
